                                PPPL Newsgroups

   PPPL newsgroups. Set your news server to news.pppl.gov to access these.

     * pppl.announce General Lab-wide announcements
     * pppl.ccf Postings about the Central Computing Facility
     * pppl.colloquia Announcements for PPPL colloquia
     * pppl.ead Engineering Analysis Division news
     * pppl.general General PPPL news
     * pppl.ingres PPPL INGRES news
     * pppl.library PPPL Library news
     * pppl.news.aps News from APS and AIP
     * pppl.news.ersug News from Energy Research Supercomputing User Group
     * pppl.news.infomac Cross postings from the infomac mailing list
     * pppl.news.tex Cross postings from various TeX mailing lists
     * pppl.news.texhax TeXhax mailings
     * pppl.outage For operations to announce upcoming network/systems
       outages
     * pppl.sun.announce PPPL Sun announcements
     * pppl.tftr.news TFTR news
     * pppl.tftr.physics PPPL TFTR physics news
     * pppl.theory.announce Important announcements for Theory Division
     * pppl.theory.general General interest postings for Theory Division
     * pppl.tpx.news Tokamak Physics Experiment news
     * pppl.transp.developer PPPL Transp developer news
     * pppl.transp PPPL Transp Users News
     * pppl.unix PPPL Unix news
     * pppl.unixcluster PPPL Unix Cluster news
     * Other newsgroups from Princeton Univ. and NERSC
